<span id="freeTextContainer10289161533479614594">6/5 stars <br/><br/>Muhammad Yunus is a once in a generation man. I paused at multiple times to make notes and reflect on self-evident truths on not just poverty alleviation, but also the nature of business operations and humanity at large. Excellent start to reading this year and intrigued to learn more about microcredit.</span>

