<span id="freeTextContainer872878152772910564">I LOVED THIS BOOK -- six stars. It tells the story of Grameen and microcredit from the beginning until now.<br/><br/>Forget theories, classrooms, and endless postulating. Acting on a desire to help others will go so much further than all of aggrandized theories and reticent intentions.<br/><br/>Muhammad Yunus changed the world with a simple idea spurned from his moral sense.<br/><br/>Simple goodwill is undervalued.</span>

