<span id="freeTextContainer16486697879705619369">This is an autobiography of a great man Mohammed Yunus who is also a recipient of Nobel Peace Prize.<br/> This is a story of a miraculous work done by Dr Yunus for the upliftment of downtrodden Bangladeshis through his exceptionally creative Grameen Bank which was a path breaking experiment. <br/> The book also gives glimpses of the contemporary rural society of Bangladesh.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


